If you are a NEICE participating state please utilize NEICE for all correspondence, if you are NOT a NEICE participating state please utilize traditional mailing/electronic mailing/or UPS/FED EX. If you choose to utilize electronic correspondence(this correspondence is not secure or encrypted) please utilize the dedicated ICPC mailbox at DCFS.InterstateCompactGeneral@illinois.gov DO NOT send correspondence for referrals/placement notification or progress reports to a specified coordinator/Deputy compact administrator or Compact Administrator.
